  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali76-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">iḵtu “acca nīṭiṉum” (to.po.111) eṉṟataṉāṟ kūṭṭamuṇmai uṇarnta tōḻikku uṇmai 
            kūṟutaṟku añciya accam nīṭṭittut talaivi kūṟiyatu. itu “tiṇaimayak kuṟutaluṅ kaṭinilai yilavē” 
            eṉṉuñ cūttiravitiyāṉ (to.po.12), marutattuk kuṟiñci vantatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali76">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>puṉaiyiḻai nōkkiyum puṉalāṭap puṟañcūḻntu</l>
                <l>maṇivari taiiyunam milvantu vaṇaṅkiyu</l>
                <l>niṉaiyupu varuntumin neṭuntakai tiṟattivvū</l>
                <l>riṉaiyaḷeṉ ṟeṭuttōtaṟ kaṉaiyaiyō nīyeṉa</l>
                <l>viṉavuti yāyiṉ viḷaṅkiḻāy kēḷiṉi;</l>
                <l>cevviral civappūrac cēṭceṉṟā yeṉṟavaṉ</l>
                <l>pauvanīrc cāykkoḻutip pāvaitan taṉaittaṟkō</l>
                <l>kauvainō yuṟṟavar kāṇātu kaṭuttacol</l>
                <l>lovvāveṉ ṟuṇarāynī yorunilaiyē yuraittatai;</l>
                <l>oṭuṅkiyām pukalollēm peyartara vavaṉkaṇṭu</l>
                <l>neṭuṅkaya malarvāṅki neṟittuttan taṉaittaṟkō</l>
                <l>viṭuttavar virakiṉṟi yeṭuttacoṟ poyyākak</l>
                <l>kaṭintatu milaiyāynī kaḻaṟiya vantatai;</l>
                <l>varitēṟṟāy nīyeṉa vaṇaṅkiṟai yavaṉpaṟṟit</l>
                <l>terivēyttōṭ karumpeḻutit toyyilcey taṉaittaṟkō</l>
                <l>puripunam māyattār poyyāka veṭuttacol</l>
                <l>luritteṉa vuṇarāynī yulamantāy pōṉṟatai;</l>
                <l>eṉavāṅku,</l>
                <l>aritiṉi yāyiḻā yatutēṟṟal puriporuṅ</l>
                <l>kaṉṟunam vatuvaiyu ṇamarceyva tiṉṟīṅkē</l>
                <l>tāṉayan tiruntativ vūrāyi ṉevaṉkolō</l>
                <l>nāñceyaṟ pāla tiṉi.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l></l>
            </lg>
        </div>
